<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Mauritania">Mauritania</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_contemporary_Islamic_scholars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Mauritania"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
