<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Senegal">Senegal</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_contemporary_Islamic_scholars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Senegal"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
