<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Morocco">Morocco</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_contemporary_Islamic_scholars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Morocco"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
